OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783720151
OL,3,CIs this the hottest Wimbledon on
OL,4,Crecord?
OL,6,FAfter nearly a week of heatwave
OL,7,Fconditions in many areas, including
OL,8,FSW19, is it a historically hot year
OL,9,Ffor Wimbledon?
OL,11,FHow hot has it been at Wimbledon?
OL,13,FWe're currently on heatwave number
OL,14,Fthree in as many months.
OL,16,FAs the temperature climbs to 35-36C or
OL,17,Fmore again on Friday, it'll mean we've
OL,18,Fhad more days of 35C + than any other
OL,19,Fyear to date. We're not even halfway
OL,20,Fthrough the summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
