FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783720151
OL,3,CIs this the hottest Wimbledon on
OL,4,Crecord?
OL,6,FThis latest heatwave has coincided
OL,7,Fwith the start of Wimbledon and is due
OL,8,Fto last into the finals weekend, with
OL,9,Fthe hint of a slight breeze after the
OL,10,Fexceptionally calm and dry conditions
OL,11,Fof late.
OL,13,FIs this Wimbledon's hottest tournament
OL,14,Fever?
OL,16,FIt's certainly one of the hottest on
OL,17,Frecord for the world-renowned
OL,18,Ftournament, but we won't know for sure
OL,19,Fif it is the hottest ever until the
OL,20,Fweekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
