OL,3,CIs this the hottest Wimbledon on
OL,4,Crecord?
OL,6,FIn recent years, Wimbledon has used an
OL,7,Fon-site team supported by MeteoFrance,
OL,8,Fthe national weather provider of
OL,9,FFrance.
OL,11,FIt's also worth noting that all
OL,12,Ftemperatures are taken in the shade
OL,13,Ffor consistency. If you factor in
OL,14,Fdirect sunshine, add around another
OL,15,F10C for those without shade on Centre
OL,16,FCourt.
OL,26,@oD@^rr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
