PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783720151
OL,3,CIs this the hottest Wimbledon on
OL,4,Crecord?
OL,6,FA report on Grand Slams by Climate
OL,7,FCentral found that an increased number
OL,8,Fof hot days has resulted in
OL,9,Ftournaments introducing heat policies
OL,10,Fto protect players.
OL,12,FThis includes guidelines such as
OL,13,FWimbledon's heat rule that allows a 10-
OL,14,Fminute break when the heat stress
OL,15,Findex is at or above 30.1C. The heat
OL,16,Fstress index combines air temperature,
OL,17,Fhumidity, and surface temperature,
OL,18,Frather than using air temperature
OL,19,Falone. It was initially introduced in
OL,20,F2015 and has been refined.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
