PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783720151
OL,3,CIs this the hottest Wimbledon on
OL,4,Crecord?
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe heat rule does not apply if
OL,12,Fmatches are played with the roof
OL,13,Fclosed on Centre Court or No 1 Court
OL,14,Fas the indoor environment is climate-
OL,15,Fcontrolled. It also does not apply to
OL,16,Fdoubles matches.
OL,18,FThe heat stress index is measured 30
OL,19,Fminutes before play, then again at
OL,20,F2:00 pm and 5:00 pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
