OL,3,CIs this the hottest Wimbledon on
OL,4,Crecord?
OL,6,FThis year's extreme heat also affected
OL,7,Fspectators, with several matches
OL,8,Fbriefly interrupted because fans
OL,9,Fneeded medical assistance in the
OL,10,Fstands, highlighting that conditions
OL,11,Fcan be challenging for everyone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
